      "paper_id": "PMC_extracted",
      "text_span_id": "results_4",
      "text": "Pseudomonas aeruginosa biofilms on stainless steel were affected by N-acetyl-L-cysteine, as both the fast and intermediate Maxwell elements were reduced by more than 50%",
